sequencing_info.library_screen: 40 uL reaction containing 10 uL of bead purified digested product, 18uL of nuclease-free water, 8uL of 5X secondary PCR master mix, and 5 uL of 10 uM TruSeq i5/i7 barcode primers
sequencing_info.pcr_cond: 10 min at 95C, 13 cycles for high density samples (or 15 cycles for low density samples) of 15 sec at 98C and 75 sec at 60C
